org.apache.cassandra.io.sstable

Interface ISSTableScanner

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, BasePartitionIterator<UnfilteredRowIterator>, CloseableIterator<UnfilteredRowIterator>, java.util.Iterator<UnfilteredRowIterator>, UnfilteredPartitionIterator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BigTableScanner, BigTableScanner.EmptySSTableScanner

    public interface ISSTableScanner
extends UnfilteredPartitionIterator
    An ISSTableScanner is an abstraction allowing multiple SSTableScanners to be chained together under the hood. See LeveledCompactionStrategy.getScanners.
